    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_620_4",
    "text": "1.亲突然站定，朝(cháo zhāo)幽深的树林望了又望。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.122,
      0.23872742494916876,
      0.602,
      0.2569070685324722
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_620",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_620_15",
    "text": "1.认识生字；会写生字。 2.默读课文，理解课文 内容。 3.积累优美词语，练习 用“我会读”中的词语 说句子。 4.体会“父亲”的爱鸟之 情和“我”的护鸟心愿。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.7393333333333333,
      0.24351154168161704,
      0.9086666666666666,
      0.41095562731730656
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_620",
    "order": 8
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_620_5",
    "text": "2.黎(ní lí)明时，所有的鸟抖(dǒu dòu)动着浑的羽翎。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.12133333333333333,
      0.26312642028465494,
      0.6293333333333333,
      0.2832197105609377
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_620",
    "order": 9
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_620_6",
    "text": "3.树林过夜的鸟总(zhǒng zǒng)是一群。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.122,
      0.28800382729338597,
      0.504,
      0.30761870589642387
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_620",
    "order": 10
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_620_7",
    "text": "二、看拼音，写词语。",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
